Installation instructions
-------------------------

== Requirements ==
If you find that this script works with any older versions of these 
applications, please drop me a note at and@vmn.dk.

*nix system (although you shouldn't have many troubles getting this to run 
under ActiveState)

Perl version 5.8.8 or later

Fortune (for !fortune functionality)

= Perl modules =
Net::IRC v.0.75
DBI v.1.52
DBD::SQLite v.1.12
LWP::UserAgent v.5.805

== Installation ==
1) su -c "make install"
2) refresh your path (or just run /usr/local/bin/anna)
3) type "anna"
4) ???
5) PROFIT!!!

See HELP or anna.pl --help for more info on how to run Anna^
